Gymshark Train
We train. We motivate. We grow. Together.
Step up your game and join the family, so we can #GymsharkTrain together 🦈

Get ready to sweat with @scottw_jordan 💦 This epic full body workout can be done right from your living room floor. All you need is a set of dumbbells 💪 Let’s go Gymshark fam 🦈

#Gymsharktrain

#Gymsharktrain

#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Get ready to make that full body work with this powerful at-home HIIT workout from @mrandmrsmuscle 💪 
Tag a friend who you would duo this with!
#Gymsharktrain

Please only take part in the workout if you are medically and physically fit and have not been advised not to participate by a qualified medical professional. If your health or fitness changes adversely in any way before, during and/or after the workout please seek and follow medical advice without delay.

node.text:
@wozldn brings you a 🔥 full body workout to celebrate the last day of #Gymshark66! Expect 30 minutes of dynamic and energetic H.I.I.T exercises – you're defo going to need some water 🥵

Please only take part in the workout if you are medically and physically fit and have not been advised not to participate by a qualified medical professional. If your health or fitness changes adversely in any way before, during and/or after the workout please seek and follow medical advice without delay.

node.text:
Get ready for a fast + fiery @_meccca workout to grow those legs + glutes! 🍑
1️⃣ Landmine squat (4x10)
2️⃣ Dumbbell reverse lunge to knee lift (4x10 each leg)
3️⃣ Bench sit to squat jump (4x10)
Tag your gym squad so they can grow with you 👭
#GymsharkTrain

node.text:
Before you try this killer shoulder workout, make a mental note to focus on that mind-muscle connection with every rep. It's the 🔑
Swipe + save:
1️⃣ Around the world into thumbs up lateral raise (3x8) 
2️⃣ Arnold press (3x10)
3️⃣ Single arm rear delt row (3x12)
4️⃣ Rear delt pull (3x10)
5️⃣ Alternating lateral raise (3x8)
📸: @alexricee
#GymsharkTrain

node.text:
✔️ Believe in yourself
✔️ Be determined
✔️ Train hard
📸: @katie_t86
#GymsharkTrain

You don’t always need a gym to get a good workout in 💪
This at-home workout from @odinmkalvo is all you need for core, balance and mobility gains:
1️⃣ Sit-ups + Leg raises (3x20 each)
2️⃣ Back raise + Side to side + Arm raise + 15’ hold (3x20 each)
3️⃣ Push ups (3x20)
4️⃣ Pistol squats (3x10)
#GymsharkTrain

node.text:
Get ready to smash those leg + glute goals with this save-worthy routine:
🍑 Sumo deadlifts
🍑 RDLs
🍑 Hip thrusts with hold on last rep
🍑 Glute med cable kickbacks
Rep ranges and sets can be specific to your goals and the weight you’re using 🙌
📸: @legswithshmegs
#GymsharkTrain
